dininginfo.name: Roots
dininginfo.description: Roots is the university's first exclusively vegan eatery and lounge. Located on the Muir College campus below Pines Restaurant, Roots has a clean, modern feel that reflects its menu perfectly. Diners can choose from a delicious variety of hearty entrees, sides, and smoothies.
